      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mapping from experimental setup parameters to CFD boundary conditions formally documented; dimensional analysis confirms similarity; any scaling effects quantified.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency mapping document produced. Boundary conditions transferred from experimental protocol to CFD setup by analyst judgment without documented traceability matrix. Similarity analysis not performed. Equivalency factor not assessed; critical epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1."
